com.jaxio.celerio.template

Class ImportsHolder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jaxio.celerio.template.ImportsHolder

  • public class ImportsHolder
extends Object
    The ImportsHolder accumulates imports needed by the generated java files. It handles duplicate entries, ignores well know imports such as import java.lang.* or imports from the current package.
